THIRD-PARTY NOTICES

This package bundles a Rust core (compiled via the Native Assets pipeline)
in addition to its Dart code, so the third-party libraries that ship in the
final artefact span two ecosystems. Direct dependencies of each are listed
below with their SPDX license expressions and upstream repositories.

Transitive dependencies are not enumerated here; the authoritative,
fully-resolved sets live in `pubspec.lock` (Dart) and `rust/Cargo.lock`
(Rust). Every transitive crate and package in those lockfiles is licensed
under one of the permissive licenses referenced in this file
(MIT, Apache-2.0, BSD-3-Clause, ISC, Zlib, CDLA-Permissive-2.0).

